author: ate
msg: Fixing servlet filter support (among others) for dispatched servlets by allowing (first) attribute access to the *current* servletrequest parent.
(how "nice" the TCK doesn't check these kind of standard servlet (filters) interactions...)
This fix gets Wicket portlet support working again.
